results.name: a(0) = 0; for n>0, minimal prime factor of n, or 1 if n is 1 or a prime.
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..20000
program: (PARI) a(n) = if (n==0, 0, if (n==1, 1, if (isprime(n), 1, factor(n)[1,1]))) \\ _Michel Marcus_, Jun 03 2013
